    <section id="import-auto-idm561726336">
      <title>Job interviews  </title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm381410560">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm386713904">It’s really important to prepare for a job interview. You should be confident and make sure the interviewer knows you want the job. You need to make the interviewer think you are the best person for the job. You should arrive early for an interview and wear smart clothes. You should smile and be polite. You should talk about your experiences and skills. You should have some good questions to ask at the end of the interview.</para>
      <section id="import-auto-idm545679488">
