    <section id="import-auto-idm611988928">
      <title>At the interview  </title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm203078064">It is useful to know some job interview questions.</para><section id="import-auto-idm424333072">
        <title>Ask the following questions to a partner </title>
        <para id="import-auto-idm205606640">.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm201242192">1) Tell me about yourself.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm174731008">2) What are your strengths? Skills?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm205343328">3) What is your major weakness?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm610170960">4) What are your career goals?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm520444736">5) What things are most important to you?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm202400368">6) Do you prefer to work alone or as part of a team? Why?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm196915376">7)  What are your hobbies and past times?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm588685984">8) What are your qualifications?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm583894784">9) What do you know about are company?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm208467648">10) What salary do you expect?</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm435981264">.</para>
      </section>
