      <section id="import-auto-idm440095200">
        <title>Read the text and answer the questions. </title>
        <para id="import-auto-idm570060512">.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm202498448">Each apprentice would be expected to perform workshop duties, these would include checking and maintaining tools and equipment and cleaning the workshop. The apprentice would also be expected to make tea and coffee for the skilled tradesmen. As an apprentice you would work eight hours a day with two thirty minute breaks. The working day would start at seven o’clock and finish at four o’clock. College would be attended in the evenings. </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm548044336">.</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm425236176">1) What are the apprentice’s duties?................................................. </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm371527904">2) How many hours a day would the apprentice work? ..............................................</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm443620064">3) How many breaks in a day would the apprentice have?.........................................</para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm361496304">4) When would the apprentice attend college?.................................................. </para>
        <para id="import-auto-idm1386806752">.</para>
      </section>
