    <section id="import-auto-idm578681152">
      <title>End of section assignment  </title>
      <para id="import-auto-idm548049632">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm544374752">Do you know of any construction sites near where you live?</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm553864368">Find out about at least one building project that you know. It could be a small project or a very large one.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm360041968">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm541038624">What trades can you see? What are they building? What is the name of the company? Would you like to work for this company? Why? Write a short essay in English about what you found out. </para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm413209616">.</para>
      <para id="import-auto-idm417771808">Note: Do not enter the construction site without permission or safety clothing.</para>
